6) HOW NEW MODULES FIT

Placement:
- UI: src/views/<Feature>.tsx + src/hooks/use<Feature>.tsx
- API: apps/api/src/modules/<feature>/
- Edge: supabase/functions/<feature>/index.ts
- DB: supabase/migrations/<timestamp>_<feature>.sql

Registration:
- UI route registration in src/App.tsx#L105
- API provider/controller registration in apps/api/src/app.module.ts#L24
- Edge function auto-discovery in workflow + verify_jwt in supabase/config.toml
- Migration picked by migration workflow

Data contracts:
- Protected API calls: invokeProtectedApi
- Protected edge calls: invokeProtectedFunction
- Keep typed response shapes and explicit error bodies
- Reuse query keys + invalidations for cache coherence

Reusable utilities:
- useUserRole, useTenantMembership, ProtectedRoute
- runtimeUrls
- authBridge
- Edge shared modules: _shared/cors.ts, _shared/authTenant.ts, _shared/rateLimiter.ts

Conventions:
- Hooks: useXxx
- Views: PascalCase
- Query keys: array literals
- Errors: user-actionable Error messages + UI toast/card surfacing
- Testing: current automation limited; RLS script exists at scripts/test-rls.js#L45

Constraints/gotchas:
- Hybrid Next + legacy Vite artifacts coexist:
  src/main.tsx#L1, index.html#L28
- Build currently tolerates type/lint issues:
  next.config.ts#L5
- Tenant DB secret decryption is stubbed:
  apps/api/src/infra/database/tenant-db.manager.ts#L118
